  <title translate="true">I cannot add an Angle (or Linear) Motion Dimension FB. Why?</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Motion Dimension FB<keyword translate="true">Cannot Add!</keyword><keyword translate="true">Problems</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">I cannot add an Angle (or Linear) Motion-Dimension FB. Why?</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_" translate="true">Motion-Dimension command and Elements.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">You must select three elements when you add a Motion-Dimension FB for a Rocker. They are:</text></para>
    <list id="2" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">A Pin-Joint...</text></li>
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">...followed by two Line sketch-elements.</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">However, you may find you cannot select one of the Lines to complete the command. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">This can happen when:</text></para>
    <list id="3" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">there is already a Motion-Dimension FB at the Pin-Joint</text></li>
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">the Point used by the Pin-Joint is not a child to Line radiating from the Pin-Joint.</text></li>
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">the Pin-Joint that you select is not a Pin-Joint between the two Lines you want to select.</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Read this topic: </text><text styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">&#32;</text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-FB-Motion-Dimension" anchor="AddMotDimeSpecial" styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">Add Motion-Dimension</link><text styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">.</text></para>
  </body>
</topic>
